  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Typhoon Mangkhut Response (Phase Two)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">-Distribution of cash grants to 500 vulnerable families affected by Typhoon Mangkhut
-Support to local organisations in leading community projects for recovery and resilience
-Strengthening community/POs and promoting community-based DRRM/ locally-led disaster preparedness and response</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will support families affected by typhoons in addressing their basic needs following their losses due to a typhoon. Similarly, it will help communities in recovering from the disaster by leading and managing small projects aimed that will strengthen their preparedness and coping capacities.</narrative>
  </description>
